Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在座的十位同学将无法参加今年的竞赛会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  请把这当做是你们自身成长的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在在你们心中的不甘与难过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.39,0:00:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是出场成员所无法体会到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 可以说你们已经有所成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要不忘这份心情  努力投入到练习中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你们会取得更大的进步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请把这次经验当成你们的宝贵经历
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后  帮助你们跃向成功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是长笛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是悠风号的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆号的呢{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆号{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  就是这首曲子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说是让我们好好练习  直到能演奏出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是单簧管…还有大号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…单簧管是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,单簧管的给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  老师口才还真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他那么一说  我们也只有拿出干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,况且还是帅哥对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我倒没那样觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  圆号的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆号的是哪张啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}等一下哦\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  明明就是帅哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.33,0:02:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:02:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在大家都有了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们马上拿上乐器练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  之前部长不是让我们先把名字定下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fs70\3c&H935004&\pos(980,720)}{\bord1.5\blur2\fad(500,0)}起跑 Monaka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fn@方正准圆_GBK\fs50\b0\1a&H50\bord0\frz-90\move(1770,100,3000,100,30,7829)}\h\h\h\h队伍名考量\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}替补选手\N{\fscy540}\N{\fscy100}支援选手\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}替补组合\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}Team next\N{\fscy500}\N{\fscy100}Fortune team\N{\fscy400}\N{\fscy100}Team miscast\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}The hope\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}还有明天\N{\fscy500}\N{\fscy100}心的呐喊\N{\fscy480}\N{\fscy100}Dive to sound\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}天河星\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}Sound Of Fairy\N{\fscy530}\N{\fscy100}二汤队\N{\fscy480}\N{\fscy100}B队\N{\fscy550}\N{\fscy100}大五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面的也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面几个已经和吹奏乐没关系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说  这大五郎是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家小狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家认真点好不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还全写上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好能取个凸显出我们十个人的  有个性的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大五郎这名字超有个性哦
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.60,0:03:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}个性啊\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}那凸显我们十人的地方在哪\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}那个…\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么把我们名字的首字连起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yo  ka  hi  fu  mo  na  ta  ka  na  ka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没法整理成像样的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只把学姐们的名字首字连起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中川夏纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,森田忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我自己  加部友恵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,na  mo  ka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ka  mo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mo  na  ka{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(960,990)}（与日语最中发音相同  日本的点心豆馅糯米饼）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔  Monaka{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monaka队  不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我怎么听着像搞笑组合的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王国…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3}（摩纳哥与最中日语发音相似）\N{\r}那个是摩纳哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3}（摩纳哥为公国）\N{\r}再说也不是王国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可爱是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就到竞赛会结束为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们的队伍名就叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monaka队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  最中{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是最中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.69,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3}（最中除指那个点心外还有正当中的意思）\N{\r}「我们正处于最青春的年华」…的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是把二年级名字的首字连起来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太简单直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好吗  也容易记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.12,0:05:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确  也行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  对大家说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起我们Monaka队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会向着竞赛会和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么能帮得上的  请尽管告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  像这样无法参加合奏练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才切实地感受到自己是落选之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泷老师不是说了吗  把这份不甘投入到练习中去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我们也还是有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  好好练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs60\1a&H60\frx12\fry30\frz329.568\move(203,351,346,351,23,6029)}Monaka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs180\1a&H60\frx6\fry16\frz327.206\move(505,870,580,870,21,2481)}Monaka
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  Monaka队  加油{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不错呢  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卓柏卡布拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶月  练习是在二楼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一鼓作气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不练习吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…现在在休息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  底下有滑轮的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要下了楼梯  就很轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我帮你拿到楼梯下面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…你能帮我托住下面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了  你放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西一个人拿一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤你是进了高中才加入吹奏乐部的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  之前不是告诉过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  你有和我说过为什么会选大号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个倒还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我一开始是想选小号的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是被明日香学姐忽悠了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被忽悠了{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说什么「这就是你命中注定的乐器」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都是吹长号的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  中学的时候是圆号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  可你长号吹得好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我从以前就一直想要吹长号的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢爵士长号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冢本{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你加油练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么久美子情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久美子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  因为不在一起练习  所以也没法经常在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  自选曲里有一段她不太擅长…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想  合奏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冢本不是就在她边上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶月你…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挖墙脚{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  你坦白地说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  真的不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  喜欢一个人不需要在意什么规则
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord2.5\fsp3\pos(927,990}Sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绿辉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手刀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想他们因为我而变得关系尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果我去多嘴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只怕事态会变得更糟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很不擅长呢  这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前就觉得恋爱是件很麻烦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  好麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉  这方面一窍不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表白什么的  要是没做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少比什么都不做要强得多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶月你很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很酷  超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去便利店啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你又要去扭扭蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢  我请你吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就买个贵点的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护身符吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将我们的心意装在这里面送给竞赛会的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在电视里看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也有在考虑做吉祥物之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过要做50个以上会不会太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家分一分也没多少啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉拉想要做可爱点的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知了怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么选这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么还是…选和我们队伍名相关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的会注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要的就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个怎么回事  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落选的时候我还以为之后的练习会轻松一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是忙点比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闲下来总会觉得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说  刚才你拿的是谁的签啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁的  谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏纪学姐有和男生交往过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…保密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有悠风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多数是久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  突然这是做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道  就是觉得你很让人心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很热的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖  乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要让自己后悔  这就是我现在唯一能告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能加入低音组真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们来得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  仔细打包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和昨天的东西一起放到走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶月  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久美子  高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来得真早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们二个的校服好干净啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  送去洗衣店洗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,领巾也换了新的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说  久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的领巾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说  我就想会不会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我机智吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真机智呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.78,0:15:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一直在很努力练习不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连鼻血都练出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前些时候在河那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有听到你的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力支援你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  系好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧  还要吹奏热身不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点  慢点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个搬过去就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先从打击乐器开始往里搬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  搬大号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来搬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须得从新手毕业才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  冢本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定在等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是大号嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大巴也出发了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们Monaka队稍微收拾一下音乐教室后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再坐电车去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了会场后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就照刚才商量好的做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬运的顺序要注意一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方要是出问题的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会影响到演奏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认真点做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monaka  Monaka
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monaka 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名为爱的找茬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看  大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的  真的有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是用心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是冢本的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是特制的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦  冢本君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么突然大叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名来你好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你们搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我们会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说是最大的鼓槌忘在社团教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没辙了  学校里现在好像一个人也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我跑过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐后面的电车赶过去  大家先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  她可是加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏纪学姐为什么会加入吹奏乐部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为感觉很高雅很帅气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不高雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,练习那么严厉  离高雅相去甚远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我还是觉得能加入真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便让我再选一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我还是会选吹奏乐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\bord0\c&H545356&\frx10\fry346\frz328.75\move(485,660,498,380,26,2195)}我会全力\N\h\h\h\h支援你的\N\h\h\h\h{\c&H774136&}去吧{\rsymbol}!{\r}{\rsymbol}!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别小看大号手的肺活量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像平常那样演奏就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  没问题吧
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\bord2.5\fsp3}赶上了哦\N{\r}\h
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶月{\rsymbol}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才跑着回去帮忙拿鼓槌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去展现一场最棒的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.82,0:21:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北宇治的各位  请上场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:02.71,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叶えたいことが溢れてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.29,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立ち止まってる暇なんてないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:14.96,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸に秘めたあこがれをフルボリュームで届けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:19.64,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行こう… クレッシェンドの向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.91,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}つまずいてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.74,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はみだしてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:34.31,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の音色を僕たちは待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:42.95,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}響け{\rsymbol}!{\r} 生まれたての夢つめ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:48.93,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大きな空へいま旅立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:54.52,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}拓け{\rsymbol}!{\r} 笑顔を味方につけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:02:00.41,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}離さない 諦めたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:05.52,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}限界さえも跳ね返す勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:09.81,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}DREAM SOLISTER
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.25,0:01:02.71,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要实现的梦想不断涌现
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.29,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}没有余暇在此止步不前
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.82,0:01:14.96,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将内心潜藏的憧憬用最大乐声传递出去
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.96,0:01:19.64,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}向前迈进 朝着Crescendo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.77,0:01:22.91,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}摔倒也没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.74,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}超过极限也无所谓
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.92,0:01:34.31,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们等待着你奏起的乐声
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.37,0:01:42.95,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}吹响 将那新生的梦想全部融入其中
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.16,0:01:48.93,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在向着广阔的天空启程
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.93,0:01:54.52,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迈进 绽放属于我们的笑容
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.64,0:02:00.41,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不想离开 也不愿放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.41,0:02:05.52,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用连极限也能轻松克服的勇气
Comment: 1,0:01:38.47,0:01:42.34,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}DREAM SOLISTER
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:17.32,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}トゥッティ  私達が心を奪う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:34.75,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マウスピースと今日のリードを選びながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.87,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}汚れたクロス紙を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:44.34,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}書き込んだスコア達が試してるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:47.95,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}青春の価値
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:52.74,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でる  教室の窓から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.34,0:22:57.12,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}繋げる  フレーズからフレーズへ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:23:01.12,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人でも欠けたらだめなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:07.78,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}音に伝わる感動  みんなで響け
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.26,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}体が歌ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:13.62,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きらめきのパッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.75,0:23:18.57,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}チューナーの揺らぎはきっと舞い上がる高揚感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:21.09,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想いをのせてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:23.77,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}楽器って赤い糸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:31.08,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}息を合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.70,oped_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}トゥッティ  私達が心を奪う
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.11,0:22:17.32,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}合奏  将我们的乐曲深入人心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.95,0:22:34.75,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}选择号嘴和今日的簧片
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.91,0:22:37.87,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}放下已经脏掉的拭布
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.87,0:22:44.34,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}尝试吹奏那描绘好的乐谱
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.67,0:22:47.95,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}绽放青春的价值
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.32,0:22:52.74,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奏响音乐  从教室的窗户传出
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.34,0:22:57.12,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}紧紧相连  从乐句到乐句
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.12,0:23:01.12,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每个人都是不可或缺的存在
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.12,0:23:07.78,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将音乐传递出去的感动  一起吹响
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.26,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用身体奏响歌曲
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.26,0:23:13.62,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}汇成闪耀的前路
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.75,0:23:18.57,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}摇摆的校音器激起层层的高涨感
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.69,0:23:21.09,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将思绪汇入
Dialogue: 1,0:23:21.09,0:23:23.77,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}名为乐器的红线
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.23,0:23:31.08,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将我们紧密相连
Dialogue: 1,0:23:33.55,0:23:37.70,oped_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}合奏  将我们的乐曲深入人心
